creator: Younode, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
◇ Let’s share what you are listening to ◇
All you have to do is connect to Spotify. Automatically, you can share the songs you're listening to with everyone. A part of you is made of music. Listen to music all the time.

◇ Discover the music you never know ◇
Do you have trouble finding the next song you want to listen to? The actions of your friends flow into a single timeline. For example, a song that your followers are interested in. This is a whole new experience of listening.

◇ Find your new friends ◇
Feel free to follow people who seem to have a good sense of style. Your own social graph. New songs to discover, inspired by your friends. An exciting experience awaits you.
descriptionShort: PULP is a music social media. Let's take a look at what people are listening to!

container.value: 2FA Intercross Creative Center, 1-1, Higashi-Sapporo 5-Jo 1-Chome, Shiroishi-ku,  Sapporo,  Hokkaido, Japan

creator: Younode, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
PULP is a music-sharing social media platform.
Connect through music.

◇ Discover new favorites◇
Check out what your friends are jamming to. Explore music beyond the typical AI recommendations, and let serendipity be your guide.

◇ Share your musical inspiration ◇
Listen in the moment, then share it with your friends. Map your musical life on PULP, and find deeper connection with your friends through shared moments.

◇ Make new friends ◇
Follow people with similar tastes. Meet new friends and experience music together. Use tokens on the app to enliven your community.
descriptionShort: PULP is a music-sharing social media platform. Connect through music.

appDetails.developerAddress: 2FA Intercross Creative Center, 1-1, Higashi-Sapporo 5-Jo 1-Chome, Shiroishi-ku,  Sapporo,  Hokkaido, Japan
appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New feature: PULP tokens
PULP Tokens are a currency that can only be used within PULP.
You can get tokens by performing various actions in the app.
We are planning to make the tokens available within the app in the future. Stay tuned!

New feature: Friend referral
It is now easier to spread PULP to your friends by sharing your referral code!
You and your friend will both get tokens when you refer someone.

Other minor bug fixes and usability improvements.
